      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1734076011,
      "version": 558,
      "versionNonce": 1513574187,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779175605838,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Browser opens webpage-> sends http\n- http gets upgraded\n- server creates client object\n- register them in hub \n- start two go routines\n\n\n Browser ---> Server Hub [readPump]\n Hub ---> Browser [writePump]\n\nuser ->message--> readpump reecives it -> sends to hub-> \nhub sends to everyone (queue message in client.send)\n\n writepump recieves this message -> writes it to browser\n \nwritePump-> using ticker (sends ping) every 54 s(defined)\nbrowser sends pong->\nreadPump -> handles pong ->resets timeout  \n(Only for connection maintenance )",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Browser opens webpage-> sends http\n- http gets upgraded\n- server creates client object\n- register them in hub \n- start two go routines\n\n\n Browser ---> Server Hub [readPump]\n Hub ---> Browser [writePump]\n\nuser ->message--> readpump reecives it -> sends to hub-> \nhub sends to everyone (queue message in client.send)\n\n writepump recieves this message -> writes it to browser\n \nwritePump-> using ticker (sends ping) every 54 s(defined)\nbrowser sends pong->\nreadPump -> handles pong ->resets timeout  \n(Only for connection maintenance )",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
